data.description: Rustic A-frame located in desirable Beaver Brook community on 5.95 acres!! Great floor plan features a cozy living room with soaring ceilings and large windows, allowing a lot of natural light in. Pellet stove for those cold, winter days. Open kitchen with eat-in bar top. Two bedrooms on main level. Upstairs primary suite with double closets, private bathroom with stand up shower and deck overlooking the property. Spacious loft area offers many possibilities. Interior laundry room. Enclosed patio/storage area. Huge outbuilding has garage parking with workshop and large covered area. Lovely setting amongst the trees for added privacy and seclusion!!
